Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with temporal logic properties and their verification. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper proposes a method for verifying properties of hybrid systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper presents an algorithm for monitoring properties. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with formal analysis of complex systems. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also relevant as the proposed method can be applied to verify properties of robotic systems.
